# Linting Standards

**Version:** 1.12.0
**Priority:** HIGH - All generated code must pass project linter
**Type:** Rule (Mandatory)

---

## Core Principle

**Generated code MUST pass the project's linter. After EVERY implementation, run the linter and resolve ALL issues before marking complete.**

---

